  <section|Proposition>

  <subsection|Proposition (命题)>

  A proposition is a declarative sentence that can be judged as <underline|either true or false.>

  "This sentence is false."is not a proposition.

  <subsection|Atomic Proposition (原子命题)>

  A proposition that does not contain any smaller part that is still a proposition.

  <subsection|Compound Proposition (复合命题)>

  A proposition that involves the <underline|assembly> of multiple propositions is called a compound proposition.

